casebody.head_matter:
In the Matter of DISCIPLINE OF Robert Allan HOLSTEIN.
No. D-2939.
Supreme Court of the United States
Oct. 31, 2016.
Robert Allan Holstein, of Chicago, Illinois, is suspended from the practice of law in this Court and a rule will issue, returnable within 40 days, requiring him to show cause why he should not be disbarred from the practice of law in this Court.
